channel.title: Zerocomfor 317 client and server restoration team
channel.description:
I am currently trying to bring back the prime era of the 06' 07' rsps. This is unofficial as of right now because it's just me and my client with an old ddsp3ced source. We will be using a cluttered butterscape client and I haven't found the "perfect" server so far (i have more experience with clients than of servers.)
What i need [code]Server: a new server source (preferably blank) that some one could start coding[/code] [code]Client: nothing so far[/code]
here is my work (i have been doing this for 2 days) [img]http://img257.imageshack.us/img257/5703/317.png[/img]
Contact: javafire@hotmail.com or you can pm me here
